#1142
On a misty path~
The world seems to be spinning benieth your feet.  You keep your eyes closed
tightly and crouch low to the ground, clutching at it in an attempt to
steady yourself.  Slowly, you begin to regain your sense of direction and
equilibrium and cautiously open your eyes.  The first thing you notice is
a stoney, gray path beneith you, wide enough to fit three humans abreast.
You glance around, starting at the empty void which lies on either side of
the stone path.  A few feet into the blackness, a strange crimson and grey
mist swirls, obscuring your vision.  Even though there are no visible
light sources, the path is well lit... You have entered the Demi-Plane of
Magic.
~
