#10000
Along the northern drop~
You travel upon a stone trail.  It looks as though it was just laid out, but
never walked upon.  A few small plants struggle to survive, growing out of
the dirt-filled cracks between the stone.  To the south, a large stone building
rises from a heavy cloud which seems to be suffocating everything about it.
The bluff drops sharply directly to your north.  Looking over the cliff, you can
see a small trail winding its way up the mountain.
~
