#10038
Wizard's Laboratory~
You have entered what you would consider a high-powered mages laboratory.
There are shelves with books surrounding the entire room, a large table with
beakers that boil and bubble over with liquids of various colors.  A floating
orb in the center of the room reveals it in a blue haze, but definately a nice
change from the rest of the keep.  A large painting of a beautiful woman about
in her late twenties is hung gloriously on the southern wall of the room.  A
smaller table in the corner of the room has many squares of alternating white
and black, and some pieces that look to be carved from the finest marble are
set upon it.
Hovering in the center of the north wall is a swirling portal of silver mist.
~
